data.title: Utah Zips Codes by Population (2024)
data.meta_description: Get a list of Utah Zip Codes by population based on Census 2022 data.
data.text:
The most populated zip codes in Utah are 84043 with 77,551, 84015 at 69,772, 84096 with 69,619, 84404 at 65,940, and 84074 with 55,917. You can get the most current Census population data for all 291 Utah zip codes, sorted from the most populous zip codes in Utah to the least, according to the 2022 American Community Survey.
